org.cripac.isee.alg.pedestrian.tracking

Class BasicTracker

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.cripac.isee.alg.pedestrian.tracking.BasicTracker
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Tracker

    public class BasicTracker
extends Object
implements Tracker
    The BasicTracker class is a JNI class of a pedestrian tracking algorithm used within the Center for Research on Intelligent Perception and Computing(CRIPAC), Institute of Automation, Chinese Academy of Science.
    Author:
    Ken Yu, CRIPAC, 2016
